            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/04/credit-bubble-update-issuance-of-clos-expected-to-hit-record-in-2014/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Credit Bubble Update – Issuance of CLOs Expected to Hit Record in 2014">Leave a comment</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/blackstone/" rel="tag">Blackstone</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/carlyle/" rel="tag">Carlyle</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/crackup-boom/" rel="tag">crackup boom</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/high-yield/" rel="tag">high yield</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/junk-bonds/" rel="tag">junk bonds</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/private-equity/" rel="tag">Private Equity</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/04/credit-bubble-update-issuance-of-clos-expected-to-hit-record-in-2014/#comments">0</a> 
